<form action="javascript:;" class="mb-0">
  <div class="p-2 bg-gray-000 rounded border mb-2">
    {{form-fields/input
        property="name"
        title="Organization name"
        changeset=changeset
        validateProperty=(action "validateProperty" changeset "name")
    }}

    {{form-fields/input
        property="slug"
        title="Slug"
        changeset=changeset
        validateProperty=(action "validateProperty" changeset "slug")
    }}

    <div class="rounded bg-yellow-000 border border-yellow-100 p-2">
      <strong>Reminder:</strong> The slug is used to identify this organization in URLs and the Percy API. If changed, you must update the <code>PERCY_PROJECT</code> environment variable in your CI service. Keep in mind, old build URLs will break if the slug is changed and a new organization can claim the old slug.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-end">
    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary shadow-purple-lg mb-0" value="Save Settings" disabled={{disabled}} onclick={{action "save"}}>
  </div>
</form>